01:34:38.680 --> 01:34:43.680
♪ Consider all the worlds
thy hands have made ♪

01:34:50.080 --> 01:34:54.802
♪ I see the stars ♪

01:34:54.920 --> 01:35:00.563
♪ I hear the rolling thunder ♪

01:35:00.680 --> 01:35:05.680
♪ Thy power throughout
