01:48:01.920 --> 01:48:07.131
and make her faith
an example to all of us?

01:48:07.240 --> 01:48:10.369
Lord, show your power to a fallen world.

01:48:10.480 --> 01:48:15.327
We know you have the power to do anything.

01:48:15.440 --> 01:48:19.331
